00:37:54,480 --> 00:37:55,440
defy gravity

576
00:37:57,140 --> 00:37:58,360
and float in the air.

577
00:37:59,660 --> 00:38:01,000
Come on, come on.

578
00:38:07,710 --> 00:38:08,550
Up.

579
00:38:12,110 --> 00:38:12,950
Up.

580
00:38:14,440 --> 00:38:15,280
Stay.

581
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:23,760
Fall.

582
00:38:26,190 --> 00:38:27,440
Wow, that's amazing!

583
00:38:27,920 --> 00:38:29,630
I didn't see that coming.

584
00:38:29,630 --> 00:38:31,390
How did you do it?

585
00:38:36,070 --> 00:38:36,910
Thank you.

586
00:38:43,630 --> 00:38:45,510
Come on, stop teasing us.

587
00:38:45,510 --> 00:38:46,630
Reveal the secret.

588
00:38:47,070 --> 00:38:48,000
Just reveal the secret.

589
00:38:51,710 --> 00:38:53,400
I learned it from a magician

590
00:38:55,110 --> 00:38:56,630
to give Chengcheng a surprise.

591
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:59,800
Let's keep some mystery for now.

592
00:39:00,480 --> 00:39:02,070
After I show Chengcheng,

593
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:04,040
I'll explain it to you.

594
00:39:06,150 --> 00:39:08,150
- How thoughtful.
- OK.

595
00:39:08,150 --> 00:39:09,480
- Let's eat.
- Eat, eat.

596
00:39:09,590 --> 00:39:11,230
Let me serve you some soup.

597
00:39:11,230 --> 00:39:12,070
Thanks, Aunt.

598
00:39:48,360 --> 00:39:50,270
