of your phone,

618
00:42:14,710 --> 00:42:16,190
but it doesn't have mine,

619
00:42:16,190 --> 00:42:18,400
so the filter can use the data

620
00:42:18,880 --> 00:42:20,320
to hide your phone.

621
00:42:21,030 --> 00:42:22,360
Got it.

622
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:29,360
Chengcheng, take a look.

623
00:42:30,480 --> 00:42:32,620
